name: Through The Wire
wikiSummary: Through the Wire is the lead single from  Kanye West's  debut album The College Dropout (2004). It samples Chaka Khan's 1985 single "Through the Fire".
wikiText:
Through the Wire is the lead single from  Kanye West's  debut album The College Dropout (2004). It samples Chaka Khan's 1985 single "Through the Fire".
